-- Hochtief, Partner Set to Win $1 Billion Parkway Project in San Francisco
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-22T08:08:55Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-22/hochtief-partner-set-to-win-1-billion-parkway-project-in-san-francisco.html
Hochtief AG said the state of
California and the San Francisco County transportation authority
have issued a notice of intent to award a PPP project worth $1
billion to a consortium around a company unit. The project is to
design, build, finance, operate and maintain the Presidio
Parkway in San Francisco, Hochtief said in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  